{"data":[{"date":"16:11 25/07","title":"Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Maradona c\u1ea7u h\u00f4n b\u1ea1n g\u00e1i tr\u1ebb","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/25/huyen-thoai-maradona-cau-hon-ban-gai-tre.jpg","new_desc":"${8_news_content2}","new_url":"","id":"4624","checkdouble":"192003"},{"date":"16:20 25/07","title":"D\u00e0n sao b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf \u0111\u00e1m c\u01b0\u1edbi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Fabregas","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/25/dan-sao-bong-da-co-mat-o-dam-cuoi-tien-ve-fabregas.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>H\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t sao s\u00e2n c\u1ecf c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf \u0111\u1ea3o Ibiza, T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9c m\u1eebng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Chelsea v\u00e0 v\u1ee3 m\u1edbi c\u01b0\u1edbi.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"D\u00e0n sao b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf \u0111\u00e1m c\u01b0\u1edbi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Fabregas h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"D\u00e0n sao b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf \u0111\u00e1m c\u01b0\u1edbi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Fabregas h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/25/Dan-sao-bong-da-co-mat-o-dam-cuoi-tien-ve-Fabregas-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Messi v\u00e0 Antonella Roccuzzo l\u00e0 kh\u00e1ch VIP c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec7c sau \u0111\u00e1m c\u01b0\u1edbi c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169 c\u00f9ng b\u00e0 x\u00e3 Daniella Semaan. Hai c\u1eb7p v\u1ee3 ch\u1ed3ng ch\u01a1i v\u1edbi nhau t\u1eeb l\u00e2u v\u00e0 v\u1eabn gi\u1eef m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t d\u00f9 Fabregas chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Chelsea thi \u0111\u1ea5u.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gia dinh Fabregas la chu nhan bua tiec. Hon le cua tien ve sinh nam 1987 va co dau sinh nam 1975 duoc to chuc hoi thang 5 vua qua, ngay khi mua giai ket thuc.\" title=\"Gia \u0111\u00ecnh Fabregas l\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e2n b\u1eefa ti\u1ec7c. H\u00f4n l\u1ec5 c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1987 v\u00e0 c\u00f4 d\u00e2u sinh n\u0103m 1975 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng 5 v\u1eeba qua, ngay khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i k\u1ebft th\u00fac.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/25/Untitled-1-9667-1532482911.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Gia \u0111\u00ecnh Fabregas l\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e2n b\u1eefa ti\u1ec7c. H\u00f4n l\u1ec5 c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1987 v\u00e0 c\u00f4 d\u00e2u sinh n\u0103m 1975 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng 5 v\u1eeba qua, ngay khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i k\u1ebft th\u00fac.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</di